{"title":"CSS实现各种奇形怪状","date":"2021-01-05T17:22:39.000Z","date_formatted":{"ll":"2021年1月5日","L":"2021/01/05","MM-DD":"01-05"},"link":"post/2021/202101/CSS实现各种奇形怪状","updated":"2021-12-16T02:17:16.298Z","content":"<h2 id=\"利用border\">利用border<a title=\"#利用border\" href=\"#利用border\"></a></h2>\n<div style=\"width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-top: 50px solid blue;\n            border-left: 50px solid red;\n            border-bottom: 50px solid pink;\n            border-right: 50px solid black;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n可以按F12看下上面这个盒子的源码 样式我写成了嵌入式的:其实原理非常简单就是一个div正方形盒子他的上下左右的border设置的很大等于这个正方形的边长的一半然后颜色设置为不同就行了,然后我们从这样一形状得到三角形就很简单了,把一部分设置成为透明就行了.\n如下可以实现各种由等边三角形组成的形状:\n<div style=\"display:flex\">\n    <div style=\"width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-top: 50px solid blue;\n            border-left: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-bottom: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-right: 50px solid transparent;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n    <div style=\"width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-top: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-left: 50px solid red;\n            border-bottom: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-right: 50px solid transparent;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n    <div style=\"width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-top: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-left: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-bottom: 50px solid pink;\n            border-right: 50px solid transparent;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n    <div style=\"width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-top: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-left: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-bottom: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-right: 50px solid black;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n    <div style=\"width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-top: 50px solid blue;\n            border-left: 50px solid blue;\n            border-bottom: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-right: 50px solid transparent;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<p>对于正方形盒子border宽度设置为边长的1/2如上,如果border宽度设置成为边长的1/4如下就可以搞出梯形了:</p>\n<div style=\"width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-top: 25px solid blue;\n            border-left: 25px solid red;\n            border-bottom: 25px solid pink;\n            border-right: 25px solid black;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n<p>如果border宽度随意设置就可以搞出各种其他的各种奇怪的形状,简直不堪入目😂:</p>\n<div style=\"display:flex\">\n    <div style=\"width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-top: 150px solid blue;\n            border-left: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-bottom: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-right: 50px solid transparent;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n    <div style=\"width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-top: 30px solid transparent;\n            border-left: 40px solid red;\n            border-bottom: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-right: 50px solid transparent;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n    <div style=\"width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-top: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-left: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-bottom: 10px solid pink;\n            border-right: 50px solid transparent;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n    <div style=\"width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-top: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-left: 25px solid transparent;\n            border-bottom: 25px solid transparent;\n            border-right: 25px solid black;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n    <div style=\"width: 100px;\n            height: 100px;\n            border-top: 25px solid blue;\n            border-left: 50px solid blue;\n            border-bottom: 50px solid transparent;\n            border-right: 50px solid transparent;\n            box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n</div>\n<hr>\n<p>如果加上border-radius并且把它的值设置正方形边长的1/2或者1/4就得到了下面两个图形:</p>\n<div style=\"width: 100px;\n        height: 100px;\n        border-top: 50px solid blue;\n        border-left: 50px solid red;\n        border-bottom: 50px solid pink;\n        border-right: 50px solid black;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n<div style=\"width: 100px;\n        height: 100px;\n        border-top: 25px solid blue;\n        border-left: 25px solid red;\n        border-bottom: 25px solid pink;\n        border-right: 25px solid black;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n<p>然后稍加改造 又可以造出鬼畜的形状:</p>\n<div style=\"width: 100px;\n        height: 100px;\n        border-top: 25px solid blue;\n        border-left: 25px solid red;\n        border-bottom: 30px solid pink;\n        border-right: 10px solid black;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n<p>其实通过border-radius可以搞出来的奇形怪状可不少,可以使用mdn的生成工具慢慢调试<a href=\"https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS/CSS_Backgrounds_and_Borders/Border-radius_generator\" target=\"_blank\">Border-radius generator</a></p>\n<p>然后通过把部分border设置为透明或者把border-radius设置的更加离谱一些又可以得到其他的形状:</p>\n<div style=\"width: 100px;\n        height: 100px;\n        border-top: 50px solid transparent;\n        border-left: 50px solid red;\n        border-bottom: 50px solid transparent;\n        border-right: 50px solid black;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n<div style=\"width: 100px;\n        height: 100px;\n        border-top: 25px solid blue;\n        border-bottom: 25px solid pink;\n        border-right: 50px solid black;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n<div style=\"width: 100px;\n        height: 100px;\n        border-top: 25px solid blue;\n        border-left: 25px solid red;\n        border-bottom: 30px solid pink;\n        border-right: 10px solid transparent;\n        border-radius: 30%;\n        box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n<h2 id=\"利用伪元素\">利用伪元素<a title=\"#利用伪元素\" href=\"#利用伪元素\"></a></h2>\n<p>如果配合伪元素::before和::after 则能够玩出更多的花样来,其实利用伪元素::before和::after无非就是盒子本身弄成一个形状然后这2个伪元素再弄成2个形状,最后三个形状拼接成某个特殊的形状我们以太极为例:</p>\n<p>可以先搞一个盒子搞成分开的半圆如下:</p>\n<div style=\"width: 100px;\n        height: 100px;\n        border-top: 50px solid blue;\n        border-bottom: 50px solid pink;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n然后再利用::before和::after画两个内外反色的圆环放在左右2处即可:\n<div style=\"display:flex\">\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\n        height: 50px;\n        border-top: 15px solid pink;\n        border-left: 15px solid pink;\n        border-bottom: 15px solid pink;\n        border-right: 15px solid pink;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        background-color:blue;\n        box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n<div style=\"width: 50px;\n        height: 50px;\n        border-top: 15px solid blue;\n        border-left: 15px solid blue;\n        border-bottom: 15px solid blue;\n        border-right: 15px solid blue;\n        border-radius: 50%;\n        background-color:pink;\n        box-sizing: border-box;\"></div>\n</div>\n<p>结果如下图所示:<br>\n<img src=\"https://search.pstatic.net/common/?src=https://i.imgur.com/YenNNXH.png\" alt=\"\" loading=\"lazy\"></p>\n<h2 id=\"利用box-shadow\">利用box-shadow<a title=\"#利用box-shadow\" href=\"#利用box-shadow\"></a></h2>\n<p>下面这个月亮其实就是一个圆形盒子的红色阴影</p>\n<div style=\"width: 80px;\n            height: 80px;\n            border-radius: 50%;\n            box-shadow: 15px 15px 0 0 red;\"></div>\n<h2 id=\"总结\">总结<a title=\"#总结\" href=\"#总结\"></a></h2>\n<p>CSS生成的各种奇奇怪怪的形状其实就是先用css的特性造出来一些基础形状,然后再对这些基础形状再进行旋转变换遮罩拼接形成更加复杂的形状.</p>\n","prev":{"title":"CSS visual formatting model","link":"post/2021/202101/CSS-VFM"},"next":{"title":"搭建Hexo博客","link":"post/2021/202101/搭建Hexo博客"},"plink":"http://blog.lipanpanx.com/post/2021/202101/CSS实现各种奇形怪状/","toc":[{"id":"利用border","title":"利用border","index":"1"},{"id":"利用伪元素","title":"利用伪元素","index":"2"},{"id":"利用box-shadow","title":"利用box-shadow","index":"3"},{"id":"总结","title":"总结","index":"4"}],"reward":true,"copyright":{"author":"李攀攀","link":"<a href=\"http://blog.lipanpanx.com/post/2021/202101/CSS实现各种奇形怪状/\" title=\"CSS实现各种奇形怪状\">http://blog.lipanpanx.com/post/2021/202101/CSS实现各种奇形怪状/</a>","license":"Attribution-NonCommercial-NoDerivatives 4.0 International (<a href=\"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-nc-sa/4.0/\" rel=\"external nofollow noopener\" target=\"_blank\">CC BY-NC-ND 4.0</a>)"},"reading_time":"576 字约 4 分钟"}